==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Anthropomorphite
<hw>An`thro*po*mor"phite</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
ascribes a human form or human attributes to the Deity or to a
polytheistic deity.</def> <au>Taylor</au>.
<specif>Specifically,</specif> <def>one of a sect of ancient heretics
who believed that God has a human form, etc.</def>
<au>Tillotson</au>.⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anthropomorphitic</ent>⟦br⟧
